68
00:09:15.400 --> 00:09:17.870
My grandpa told me stories when I was a kid

69
00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:20.670
About monsters that he fought in the war

70
00:09:20.740 --> 00:09:21.770
So there you go.

71
00:09:22.310 --> 00:09:26.080
