75
00:09:34.860 --> 00:09:37.260
And he chased them off into the woods

76
00:09:37.820 --> 00:09:40.690
And the coroner said he had a heart attack

77
00:09:41.030 --> 00:09:43.030
And the cops said

78
00:09:44.570 --> 00:09:47.070
dogs went for the soft parts.

79
00:09:48.400 --> 00:09:52.510
The DNA had wounds of animals

80
00:09:52.940 --> 00:09:55.440
so thats case closed.

81
00:09:56.280 --> 00:09:59.050
He sounds like an extraordinary gentleman.

82
00:09:59.650 --> 00:10:01.750
Were you very close?

83
00:10:02.150 --> 00:10:03.450
Puerto Rico.

84
00:10:03.780 --> 00:10:05.150
Here

85
00:10:05.850 --> 00:10:08.790
There is a lake where the water glows in the dark.

86
00:10:09.460 --> 00:10:13.230
And a secret tunnel. Thats where I hid from the monsters

87
00:10:13.730 --> 00:10:16.000
He used to babysit me a lot.

88
00:10:16.660 --> 00:10:19.570
And when I was with him I felt special.

89
00:10:21.840 --> 00:10:23.070
Abe.

90
00:10:23.570 --> 00:10:26.370
Its like 11 o'clock. What is he doin up?

91
