Im going to be an explorer. Grandpas told me about my first voyage.

92
00:10:32.250 --> 00:10:35.250
Everything has already been discovered. buddy.

93
00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:45.630
Pay no attention to your father. He knows bubkiss. Come tegrisco... off to bed.

94
00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:56.770
Can you tell me a story

95
00:10:57.040 --> 00:10:58.200
The usual?

96
00:10:58.910 --> 00:11:00.570
Okay

97
00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:04.280
Once upon a time there was a little boy

98
00:11:04.650 --> 00:11:06.580
where's the pictures?

99
00:11:07.280 --> 00:11:08.380
Pictures.

100
00:11:15.520 --> 00:11:19.430
Once upon a time a little boy called Abe

101
00:11:19.860 --> 00:11:21.290
That was you.

102
00:11:21.630 --> 00:11:28.370
That was me and he lived in a lovely children's home on an little island near Wales.

103
00:11:28.870 --> 00:11:31.240
Where the sun shone every day.

104
00:11:31.770 --> 00:11:34.270
The Headmistress. Miss Peregrine....

105
00:11:34.680 --> 00:11:36.680
Was very clever.

106
00:11:37.140 --> 00:11:38.610
and she smoked my pipe

107
00:11:38.980 --> 00:11:41.250
She could turn into a bird

108
00:11:42.150 --> 00:11:45.180
It was a home for special children

109
00:11:45.850 --> 00:11:47.590
Like Bronwyn...

110
00:11:48.020 --> 00:11:49.860
and Victor

111
00:11:50.560 --> 00:11:53.460
They were both as strong as ten men.

112
00:11:53.930 --> 00:11:55.160
And Hugh

113
