Hugh had bees living inside him.

114
00:11:59.870 --> 00:12:02.570
Where is Emma? She could float.

115
00:12:03.470 --> 00:12:06.640
She was lighter than air.

116
00:12:07.310 --> 00:12:12.650
She had to wear special shoes made of lead
to keep her from floating away.

117
00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:14.810
Where is she now?

118
00:12:15.180 --> 00:12:16.580
She's still on the Island. I believe

119
00:12:18.050 --> 00:12:22.620
My mom and papa sent me there. to live with the special children.

120
00:12:23.060 --> 00:12:26.260
And now Tegrisco time to sleep.

121
00:12:26.660 --> 00:12:28.290
He used to call me Tegrisco.

122
00:12:28.660 --> 00:12:30.830
Its Polish. for little tiger.

123
00:12:31.270 --> 00:12:34.800
Couldn't have picked a less appropriate nickname.
I was always a chicken.

124
00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:38.000
Why your mom and dad send you away?

125
00:12:38.610 --> 00:12:42.110
Where we lived in Poland. it was not safe.

126
