128
00:12:47.080 --> 00:12:48.850
Huge ones.

129
00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:56.660
With long arms and no eyes. And tentacles like this.

130
00:12:58.560 --> 00:13:03.530
The dumb thing was. for years I actually believed his stories

131
00:13:04.770 --> 00:13:07.470
This is Millard. he's invisible.

132
00:13:13.870 --> 00:13:16.610
My teacher says they are trick photos.

133
00:13:17.640 --> 00:13:19.710
And did you believe her?

134
00:13:20.550 --> 00:13:24.880
Dad says that you get in one of those places that you were traveling.

135
00:13:25.490 --> 00:13:28.050
I would never lie to you. Tegrisco.

136
00:13:28.490 --> 00:13:30.060
