Jake. You were a lot closer to him than I ever was

154
00:15:03.220 --> 00:15:06.520
He was a wonderful grandpa. But not...not such a great dad. you know?.

155
00:15:09.120 --> 00:15:13.730
Never seemed to pick a job that didn't involve late nights and long trips away though.

156
00:15:14.430 --> 00:15:18.970
Me and Aunt Sussie I always kinda thought he was maybe cheating on our mom.

157
00:15:21.270 --> 00:15:26.510
I am sorry. buddy. I know how much you worshipped him but there it is.

158
00:15:33.810 --> 00:15:35.380
Surprise!!

159
00:15:35.750 --> 00:15:37.220
Happy Birthday. cousin Jake.

160
