Can't wait.

163
00:15:52.770 --> 00:15:54.500
Its aunt Sussie.

164
00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:57.240
Thought you might want to open this one.

165
00:15:58.170 --> 00:16:00.270
Its from your grandpa

166
00:16:00.770 --> 00:16:04.780
Found it while I was packing up. I figured he meant to give it to you someday.

167
00:16:07.650 --> 00:16:08.450
Thanks

168
