"Complete Essays and other writings of Ralph Waldo Emerson."

169
00:16:26.070 --> 00:16:32.810
To Jake and the worlds he has yet to discover

170
00:16:41.650 --> 00:16:43.150
My dearest Abe. "

171
00:16:43.520 --> 00:16:45.750
I hope this card finds you well

172
00:16:46.090 --> 00:16:48.820
The children and I yearn to hear your news.

173
00:16:49.160 --> 00:16:51.320
I do hope you will visit us again soon

174
00:16:51.660 --> 00:16:53.360
We should so love to see you."

175
00:16:53.690 --> 00:16:56.900
With admiration. Alma Peregrine. "

