And there is no way I'm putting my life on hold to take you to Wales.

184
00:17:18.920 --> 00:17:20.650
Dad could take me.

185
00:17:21.260 --> 00:17:24.860
And he can even look at birds... work in his book

186
00:17:25.260 --> 00:17:27.260
It means you get a break.

187
00:17:27.730 --> 00:17:31.730
And as Dr. Golan said. Maybe I can move on.

188
00:17:32.170 --> 00:17:33.930
Like closure.

189
00:17:34.800 --> 00:17:39.740
Having an opportunity to see this Children's Home and separate fantasy from reality.

190
00:17:40.070 --> 00:17:45.880
May be useful and at the very least a trip like this provides a chance to

191
