242
00:21:10.350 --> 00:21:12.920
I will break the ice like a burning blade.

243
00:21:14.450 --> 00:21:16.860
Yes. it is. it is good.

244
00:21:18.260 --> 00:21:20.630
Should we take the shortcut. D. We'll get there quicker.

245
00:21:21.060 --> 00:21:22.330
Take it from me.

246
00:21:23.130 --> 00:21:24.300
