no. I've been following you much further than that!

792
01:19:29.110 --> 01:19:35.619
Dr. Golan?! - Sometimes when
it suits me... the breadth of

793
01:19:35.620 --> 01:19:43.620
my peculiarity is purely limited by my imagination .
. the only thing I can't change... is my eyes.

794
01:19:54.670 --> 01:20:02.670
Mr. Barron. How do you do? I saw you. at
