901
01:43:27.520 --> 01:43:33.249
You are not serious? - Do I not look
serious? Do I not look like a man who has.

902
01:43:33.250 --> 01:43:38.959
Trudged the globe looking for just one
more eye to eat in hopes of regaining ..

903
